, fuck that shit, never sewing with it again!</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/bri4Uu8.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>This was my inspiration, a 1960s dress from the designer Lanz. You can kinda see why it’s been on my mind for years! Mine is unfortunately less striking. Alas, the right fabric was almost impossible to find, so the green was the best I could do. I tried to be as faithful as I could to the original but I thought a pleated skirt would work really nicely and my neckline might be a bit lower than theirs. Also I just realised the waist has piping. Shit.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/QDZiL11.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>My back is different too because I wanted the option of wearing a bra with it but found I didn’t really need it because it’s very supportive. I constructed the lining to have an under-bust seam and I contoured it a little closer to my body to hold me in. Also as far as internals go, I added two columns of zip tie boning from armpit going to centre front. Can I just say one thing I didn’t expect was how difficult this dress is to get into because of the crossover straps? Absolute nightmare, I look like a possessed green gremlin when I’m getting dressed.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/lw9DsTv.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>You can kind of see the fabric that was gonna be on the bodice used as my pocket lining. I found a new technique to sew inseam pockets and oh my god it’s like leagues better than whatever the hell mess I was doing before. It basically involves sewing the whole pocket before insertion, then sewing it on one side, clipping corners and flipping it out, then sewing skirt panels together in one fell swoop. Yep, that settles it, I’m awful at explaining things.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/ZnZP3E7.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Regardless, this dress was a real labour of love for me and surprisingly one of my hardest makes yet. I made two test runs! I would have nailed the fit too if not for that stupid flimsy gold fabric that has zero structure behind it. At least I know for next time! Friends don’t let friends sew with lame fabric. Never again.

Anyways, I made this dress over a series of several livestreams over at https://twitch.tv/carbonchic ! Feel free to join me some time if you wanna see how I make stuff or chat sewing or heckle me or whatever :)</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/m0BCkil</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[CarbonChic]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>So early</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/wcDPgc6</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Yx5Gi45.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/wcDPgc6</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[roaduardo]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Why US has no money for social programs</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/Hei46Na</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/elqlTiR.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/Hei46Na</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[jefffffffffffffffffffffffff]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Arnold Schwarzenegger has a personal message for the Russian people</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/xDmisay</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/wk3v8Xi.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/VYqgpUl.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/wKDo5vw.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/iLYDvFp.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/uOWCGk3.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/dDpcPix.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/fgdkjcO.gi