imgur.com/gallery/hmUOYB0</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/dJ9CK1z.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>SOURCE:
https://dbr.gov.ua/news/dbr-peredalo-na-potrebi-armii-odin-mln-dolariv-ssha-viluchenih-pri-sprobi-vivezennya-ih-za-kordon

TRANSLATION:
Investigators from the State Bureau of Investigation confiscated gold and foreign currency worth about $ 1 million from an employee of the Ukrainian embassy in the EU in an attempt to smuggle it abroad.

And the funds are transferred to the state budget and can be used for the needs of the Armed Forces of Ukraine.

At the Yahodyn checkpoint of the Volyn customs of the State Customs Service on February 28 last year, DBR investigators inspected a diplomatic minibus in which almost 68,000 euros, more than 140,000 US dollars, more than 12 kilograms of gold bars, gold jewelry with a total weight of 13 8 kg, as well as a large number of cigarettes. An embassy employee tried to take all this abroad under the guise of diplomatic mail.

Based on the court decision, cash, jewelry and gold worth about $ 1 million were confiscated.

The court found the representative of the embassy guilty of committing an offense under Part 1 of Art. 483 of the Criminal Code of Ukraine and fined him UAH 26.8 million.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/hmUOYB0</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Pain9Killer]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Where do you see yourself in 10 years?</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/FzD5olc</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/pn6kPCQ.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/FzD5olc</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[VagMayo]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Incoming Russian Purge</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/KbiMA7S</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/fjXxrtr.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/KbiMA7S</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[SahoA]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Matrix</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/2nCZA4L</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/rl7qloR.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/2nCZA4L</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[MrMithrandirG]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>My Brand New Haircut</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/DepnUyC</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/vIXSvw7.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I Just got my Brand New Haircut Just now</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/DepnUyC</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[frankiemacdonald]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>10-foot sturgeon believed to be between 500-600lbs and over 100 years old.</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/ChvvxdA</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/eW7WQt5.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: aut